{"tid":412656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯外長：「北韓有核武，美國唔敢打」","createTime":"2017-09-25T00:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T01:13:28.000Z","uid":41351,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3da72e958ce44113782a9c9ade2c909b7c4077b","tid":412656,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫周日（24日）表示，美國明確了解北韓擁有核武，因此不會貿然動武。他又警告，美國必須使用更溫和的手法解決北韓核問題，否則將面對無法預測的後果，令朝鮮半島以及周邊國家，數以十萬計的無辜人民受害。 <br />\n<br />\n拉夫羅夫接受電視台訪問時稱：「美國不會空襲北韓，因為他們不只是相信北韓擁核，而是肯定北韓擁有核彈。」他又指：「我不是在為北韓辯護，我只是說出大部分人都認同的看法。」 <br />\n<br />\n拉夫羅夫強調，只有用「關愛、建議及勸告」，這些更溫和的手法，才可以解決現時北韓的危機。他警告美國一旦不遵循上述方法，只會「掉落不能預測的境況，令數以萬計，甚至十萬計的南北韓民眾受害，當然日本以至鄰近的中國及俄羅斯亦會遭殃。」 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170924/mobile/bknint-20170924234539716-0924_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170924%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170924234539716-0924_17011_001.html&d=J%2FTFY9WdWstxb25PVIE3Nmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=04fe6f82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170924/mobile/bknint-20170924234539716-0924_17011_001.html</a><br />\n美國雖有攔截系統，但非萬無一失"},{"pid":"84db40ad3e5d11b87f51196e8e015569df2b2798","tid":412656,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"朝鮮半島無核化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91411c1efa33b2cfd9a7f6763ce44eac86ba8095","tid":412656,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"關愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e7318726ee15a6d91fc47195520a982219d4d6","tid":412656,"uid":43327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:15: